<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='.9em' font-size='90'>🏗️</text></svg>">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="app-header">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-brand">
                <a href="/" class="brand-link">
                    <span class="brand-icon">🏗️</span>
                    <span class="brand-text">Go Runtime Builder</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-nav">
                <a href="/" class="nav-link active">Home</a>
                <a href="/simple" class="nav-link">Simple Generator</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">

<div class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title"><%= title %></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle"><%= subtitle %></p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/simple" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">🚀 Try the Generator Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
                <h3>Interactive Questionnaire</h3>
                <p>Answer guided questions about your feature or solution to determine the optimal setup type and configuration.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                <h3>Setup Type Resolution</h3>
                <p>Automatically determines whether you need Feature Set, Individual Feature, Solution Setup, or Agent Configuration.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
                <h3>SLDS2 Design System</h3>
                <p>Generated pages follow Salesforce design guidelines with proper styling, accessibility, and responsive design.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">🔗</div>
                <h3>Page Flow</h3>
                <p>Creates linked pages following the pattern: Home → Feature Set → Individual Features with proper navigation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="setup-types-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Setup Types</h2>
        <div class="setup-types-grid">
            <div class="setup-type-card">
                <div class="setup-type-badge feature-set-badge">Feature Set</div>
                <h3>Feature Set and Features</h3>
                <p>Group multiple features with a common Job to be Done</p>
                <ul class="setup-requirements">
                    <li>≥2 features required</li>
                    <li>Clear JTBD needed</li>
                    <li>Examples: Authentication Suite, Analytics Package</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-type-card">
                <div class="setup-type-badge feature-badge">Feature</div>
                <h3>Individual Feature</h3>
                <p>Single feature or capability</p>
                <ul class="setup-requirements">
                    <li>Customer-facing capability</li>
                    <li>Can belong to Feature Set</li>
                    <li>Examples: File Upload, Search, Notifications</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-type-card">
                <div class="setup-type-badge solution-badge">Solution</div>
                <h3>Solution / Initial Setup</h3>
                <p>Foundational automated setup</p>
                <ul class="setup-requirements">
                    <li>Automation-handled</li>
                    <li>Required for cloud function</li>
                    <li>Examples: Platform Setup, CRM Initialization</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="setup-type-card">
                <div class="setup-type-badge agent-badge">Agent Setup</div>
                <h3>Agentforce Configuration</h3>
                <p>AI-powered agent setup</p>
                <ul class="setup-requirements">
                    <li>Agentforce needed</li>
                    <li>Templates and workflows</li>
                    <li>Examples: Customer Service Bot, Sales Assistant</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Ready to Build Your Configuration?</h2>
            <p>Use the simple generator to create clean HTML pages following Salesforce design templates.</p>
            <div class="cta-actions">
                <a href="/simple" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">🚀 Try the Generator Demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



    </main>

    <footer class="app-footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Salesforce Go Runtime Builder</p>
            <p>Generate configuration screens following Salesforce design guidelines</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
